             were indicted for <rs id="t17980912-77-off459" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980912-77-off459" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980912-77-off459" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17980912-77-cd460" type="crimeDate">8th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-77-off459 t17980912-77-cd460"></join>, two linen sheets, value 12s. two linen shifts, value 12s. two linen pillow-cases, value 2s. a linen towel, value 8d. and a coarse towel, value 4d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17980912-77-victim830" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Hodges
                  <interp inst="t17980912-77-victim830" type="surname" value="Hodges"></interp>
